      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>careful about the \"resources\" thing. it's not that i don't have people to talk to, it's just that talking doesn't change the fact that i've failed. i feel like i'm just performing this version of myself for everyone else, but inside i'm just... empty. like there's nothing left to give. it's like i'm running on a battery that won't even hold a charge anymore. nothing helps. everything just feels like more noise. i just want the noise to go away for good.",
